@host = http://localhost:8080

### ============================================
### 1. 기본 로깅 - LogLevel별 출력
### ============================================

### Information 레벨 (기본)
POST {{host}}/logging
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello ZLogger!",
  "level": "information"
}

### Debug 레벨
POST {{host}}/logging
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Debug message for troubleshooting",
  "level": "debug"
}

### Warning 레벨
POST {{host}}/logging
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "This is a warning",
  "level": "warning"
}

### Error 레벨
POST {{host}}/logging
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Something went wrong",
  "level": "error"
}

### Critical 레벨
POST {{host}}/logging
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Critical system failure",
  "level": "critical"
}

### ============================================
### 2. BeginScope 중첩 예시
### ============================================

### Scope Demo - RequestId와 Step이 중첩된 scope로 기록됨
POST {{host}}/logging/scope
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Testing nested scopes"
}

### ============================================
### 3. 예외 로깅 예시
### ============================================

### Exception Demo - 스택 트레이스가 포함된 에러 로그
POST {{host}}/logging/exception
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Trigger exception for demo"
}

### ============================================
### 4. 로그인 시나리오 (BaseController 패턴)
### ============================================

### 로그인 성공 - ActionLog + InformationLog 출력
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 1,
  "token": "valid-token-abc"
}

### 로그인 실패 (잘못된 토큰) - ErrorLog 출력
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 2,
  "token": "invalid"
}

### 로그인 실패 (빈 토큰) - ErrorLog 출력
POST {{host}}/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerId": 3,
  "token": ""
}

### ============================================
### 5. 게임 시작 시나리오 (BeginScope + MetricLog)
### ============================================

### 게임 시작 성공 - BeginScope(uid) + MetricLog("GameCreated") + ActionLog
POST {{host}}/game/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid": 100
}

### 게임 시작 실패 (잘못된 uid) - Warning + ErrorLog
POST {{host}}/game/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "uid": -1
}
